[SN]TITLE[SN]
Cyclist seriously hurt after colliding with man in Edinburgh

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A cyclist is in hospital with serious facial injuries after colliding with a man in Edinburgh.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Both men are being treated at the Edinburgh Royal Infirmary.
The pedestrian suffered a minor head injury during the incident which happened on Queen's Drive at about 09:45 .
